Installation or Setup # A function is a block of organised, reusable code that is used to perform a single, related action. Functions usually &ldquo;take in&rdquo; data, process it, and &ldquo;return&rdquo; a result.
User defined function # A function defined by user.
Example in PHP
//Function definition function add ($a, $b) { $sum = $a + $b; return $sum; } //Function invokation $sum = add(1,2);
